  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the judge might even be, I believe you, honestly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I need proof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he's still running around in the [INAUDIBLE] he's backing-- oh, when he was leaving the house, he was leaving the house, at the [INAUDIBLE], and I escorted him out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he was at the door and put his hand on, I said, Egri, how's Mrs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the man got a shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he stepped out of the door and start running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you see, I was well-trained.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I indicated to [INAUDIBLE] come, come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and shooting up a half a block away, there was a car waiting for him, because we could have finished the guy off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all I needed, even today, [INAUDIBLE] he lose his head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I had to keep my cool.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can't throw it away, because there might be comes a chance where I really can finish off the son of a bitch.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but all, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it's been-- you're welcome.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she's Hannah Szenes, the girl that I wrote about, the girl who was my-- my girlfriend, and finally my-- my fiance, and so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this picture what is in front of me is in Palestine, the day when she arrived there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the first time when I met her on the streets of Cairo, she was in full, full military uniform.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how I got to know her, and the last time when I saw her, it was in Cairo.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't even have a chance to say goodbye, because our service was such on an order in two hours' time you had, you were on your way, on your-- on your mission.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
